    public static final String _1Sam_27_12 = "And Achish believed David, saying, He hath made his people Israel utterly to abhor him; therefore he shall be my servant for ever. ";
    public static final String _1Sam_28_1 = "And it came to pass in those days, that the Philistines gathered their armies together for warfare, to fight with Israel. And Achish said unto David, Know thou assuredly, that thou shalt go out with me to battle, thou and thy men. ";
